# 2.3 Types of Keywords

## 1. Short-Tail Keywords

1–2 words ke keywords.

Examples:

```text
Fire Extinguisher
Fire Alarm
Fire Safety
```

Advantages:

* High Search Volume

Disadvantages:

* High Competition
* Low Conversion

---

## 2. Medium-Tail Keywords

2–3 words ke keywords.

Examples:

```text
Fire Extinguisher Mumbai
Fire Alarm System
Fire Safety Equipment
```

Advantages:

* Medium Competition
* Better Target Audience

---

## 3. Long-Tail Keywords ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

3 ya usse zyada words wale keywords.

Examples:

```text
Best Fire Extinguisher Dealer in Mumbai

Fire Extinguisher Refilling in Virar

Fire Alarm Installation for Office

Fire NOC Consultant in Mumbai
```

Advantages:

* Low Competition
* High Conversion Rate
* Easy Ranking
* Better Leads

**Recommendation:** New websites ko Long-Tail Keywords se start karna chahiye.

---

# 2.4 Search Intent

Google sirf keywords nahi samajhta, balki user ka **intention (Intent)** bhi samajhta hai.

## 1. Informational Intent

User information chahta hai.

Examples:

```text
What is Fire Extinguisher?

How to Use Fire Extinguisher?

Types of Fire Extinguishers
```

Best Content:

* Blogs
* Guides
* Tutorials

---

## 2. Navigational Intent

User kisi specific website par jana chahta hai.

Examples:

```text
SafePro Fire Services

IndiaMART

GeM Portal
```

---

## 3. Commercial Investigation

User compare kar raha hai.

Examples:

```text
Best Fire Extinguisher Brand

ABC vs CO₂ Fire Extinguisher

Top Fire Safety Company Mumbai
```

---

## 4. Transactional Intent ⭐⭐⭐⭐⭐

User buy karna chahta hai.

Examples:

```text
Buy Fire Extinguisher Mumbai

Fire Extinguisher Dealer Near Me

Fire Extinguisher Price Mumbai
```

Ye sabse valuable keywords hote hain.

---

# 2.5 Search Volume

Search Volume batata hai ki ek keyword ko average kitni baar search kiya jata hai.

Example:

| Keyword                  | Monthly Searches |
| ------------------------ | ---------------: |
| Fire Extinguisher        |           18,000 |
| Fire Extinguisher Mumbai |            1,500 |
| Fire Extinguisher Virar  |              150 |

High Search Volume ka matlab hamesha best keyword nahi hota.

---

# 2.6 Keyword Difficulty (KD)

Keyword Difficulty batata hai ki kisi keyword par rank karna kitna difficult hai.

Example:

| KD Score | Difficulty     |
| -------- | -------------- |
| 0–20     | Easy           |
| 21–40    | Medium         |
| 41–60    | Difficult      |
| 61–100   | Very Difficult |

New websites ko Easy aur Medium KD wale keywords target karne chahiye.

---

# 2.7 Search Volume vs Competition

Ideal keyword me balance hona chahiye.

High Search Volume + Low Competition = Best Opportunity

Example:

```text
Fire Extinguisher Mumbai
```

Competition High

Example:

```text
Fire Extinguisher Refilling in Virar
```

Competition Low

Conversion High

---

# 2.8 LSI Keywords (Related Keywords)

LSI (Latent Semantic Indexing) Keywords woh related words hote hain jo Google ko topic samajhne me help karte hain.

Example:

Main Keyword:

```text
Fire Extinguisher
```

Related Keywords:

```text
ABC Fire Extinguisher

CO₂ Fire Extinguisher

Fire Safety Equipment

Fire Protection System

Fire Fighting Equipment

Fire Extinguisher Refilling
```

