# 2.10 Competitor Keyword Research

Competitor Analysis bahut important hai.

Check:

* Kaunse keywords target kar rahe hain?
* Kis page se traffic aa raha hai?
* Kaunse blogs rank kar rahe hain?
* Kaunse backlinks hain?

Isse ideas milte hain, copy nahi karni chahiye.

---

# 2.11 Keyword Placement

Keyword naturally use karo.

Best Places:

* SEO Title
* URL
* Meta Description
* H1 Heading
* H2 Heading
* First Paragraph
* Image ALT
* Conclusion
* Internal Links

Keyword Stuffing avoid karo.

